[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Velvet</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 4 ====
HEADWORD: Velvet
<hw>Vel"vet</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make like, or cover with,
velvet.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Velvetbreast</ent>⟦br⟧
